{"id": "1495322278295109632", "channel_id": "1495322278295109632", "type": 0, "author_id": "452516689225973761", "author_name": "thpdom", "author_bot": false, "content": "Hello.\n\nCurrently buying silver in morimens is done through dollars no matter where you're from, no matter the general financial situation of your country.\n\nMeaning that when the Dollar is down, a lot of silver can be purchased for a lot cheaper. And players from countries with less valuable currency, may not be able to make purchases at a reasonable price at all.\n\nThere is an already existing solution and frameworks for this, this in general may help with the games financial situation.", "timestamp": "2026-04-19T07:16:52.890000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1495322278295109632", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Regional pricing", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
